            "SeoDescription": "Transistors are discrete semiconductor devices used to switch or amplify electrical signals. Types of transistors include bipolar (BJT), RF, pre-Biased bipolar (BJT), FETs, MOSEFETs, IGBTs, JFETs, programmable, and more.",
            "ChildCategories": [
